Can Norwegians afford a house in Oslo?

Salary estimates for individuals with completed higher education (level 7-8) with any field of study.

## Selected areas: Majorstu[en, a], Frogner, Fagerborg, Bislett, Marienlyst, Sagene, Bjølsen, Nydalen, Tåsen, Grünnerløkka, St. Hanshaugen, Holmen, Torshov, Kjelsås, Sogn, Storo
## 92.77% of university graduates can afford the cheapest house in selected areas
## 44.922% of university graduates can afford the median house of 5 500 000 kr in selected areas

Relevant scenarios for NORMENT employees
